description:
Walkie Talkie Offline is an app that allows the user to talk to his friends by means of a Bluetooth or wifi connection easily. You can talk with your friends by using walkie talkie. Walkie talkie provides a two-way audio transmission to the user to talk with his friends.

Walkie Talkie Offline has been equipped with a very fast scanner. It can easily scan any active devices in its range and shows them to the user in only a small matter of time.
